Privacy Policy
Last updated October 10, 2021
Effective October 10, 2021
Our Privacy Commitment
Kiragames respects your privacy rights and recognizes the importance of protecting your
                            personal information. We are also committed to providing additional protections for children
                            who visit and/or use our Services.
Kiragames’ Apps covered by this Privacy Policy include any mobile applications (“apps”)
                            displaying or linking to this Privacy Policy.
This Privacy Policy applies only to information submitted and collected online through the
                            apps and does NOT apply to information that may be collected by Kiragames on our website or
                            offline. At this time, we do not collect any information when you use our website.
Kiragames reserves the right, at any time and without notice, to add to, change, update or
                            modify this Privacy Policy and our Terms of Use, simply by posting such change, update or
                            modification on the apps. Any such change, update or modification will be effective
                            immediately upon posting on the apps. Your continued use of any of our apps will signify
                            your acceptance of these changes.
1. Scope
Our Privacy Policy applies to the collection and processing of personal information by The
                            Kiragames Co., Ltd., and our subsidiaries and affiliated company’s action on our behalf
                            (“Kiragames” or “we”, “us”, or “our”). This Privacy Policy applies only to personal
                            information collected about you as a consumer through the Kiragames network of apps,
                            features, services, events, and communications provided by Kiragames where this Private
                            Policy is posted (“Services”). This policy does not apply to human resources data or the
                            “Kiragames” website.
Our international affiliates and third-party websites or apps that our Services link to, or
                            with whom we may have a presence, or with whom we may license use of our trademarks and
                            copyrights, may collect and use personal information for their own purposes. Where they do
                            so, their respective privacy policies apply. Please review the respective terms and privacy
                            policies of these entities to learn how they process your personal information.
2. Information Collected
We process data and analytics about the use of our services such as in-game play progress,
                            levels, games played, session length, preferred settings, in-game adverts, in-game
                            preferences, game preferences, the means to use the services, device types, the operating
                            systems, and internet service providers, and general geographic location. . For example, we
                            retrieve Daily Active Users (DAU) and device type from Google Analytics and Apple, so we can
                            understand how many users playing our games daily and from what devices our games are being
                            accessed. We also process data in relation to coarse location, gameplay content, identifiers
                            (user id & device id), purchase history, usage data (product interaction & advertising
                            data), and diagnostics.
We may access or receive information about the ways you use and interact with our Services
                            through third parties services, individuals, and the intermediaries as discussed above and
                            in section 8.
