3. Use of Cookies, Flash Cookies, Web Beacons, and Similar Technologies
We collect personal data and we may use SDKs, cookies, flash cookies, web beacons, and
                            similar technologies to collect your personal information.
4. Third Parties Services
We employ third party companies and affiliates to facilitate our Services, to provide the
                            Services on our behalf, to perform service-related services or to assist us in analyzing how
                            our service is used (such as Facebook, Apple, Google Analytics and Amazon). We may collect
                            certain information when you use our Services through these third-party service providers
                            and affiliates, for example, when you connect your account to third-party services or sign
                            in using a third-party partner (like Google Play Game Services, or iOS Game Center).
