                                    practices or the content of such sites. If you are concerned about the privacy
                                    policy of a
                                    certain third party, we recommend that you read the privacy policy of the site to
                                    which you
                                    link before you submit any personal information. By accessing any external sites,
                                    you agree
                                    to the privacy policies of those sites.
